# Question 20 (Interview Favorite)

### Interface

```java
interface Compare {
    int compare(int a, int b);
}
```

Return:

* 1 if a > b
* -1 if a < b
* 0 if equal

### Answer

```java
Compare c = (a, b) -> {

    if (a > b)
        return 1;

    if (a < b)
        return -1;

    return 0;
};
```

